{"data":[{"date":"10:10 18/06","title":"Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra 2 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Brazil sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/wenger-chi-ra-2-van-de-cua-brazil-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Wenger cho r\u1eb1ng Brazil \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</h2><h2>V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Neymar</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Brazil ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhilippe Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n sau m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat xa \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 20. Nh\u01b0ng Steven Zuber \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p. V\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u1eafc 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra 2 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau khi Brazil h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra 2 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau khi Brazil h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/wenger-chi-ra-2-van-de-cua-brazil-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wenger cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Rostov Arena. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u00f2n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn khi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ra ngo\u00e0i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarcelo v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 HLV Wenger \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng danh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Brazil b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u1ede th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Neymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao l\u1edbn. Anh ch\u00e0ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 170 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 t\u00f4i cho Neymar chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Brazil</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thiago Silva v\u00e0 Miranda xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00eam qua. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Wenger tin r\u1eb1ng Marquinhos x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMirandan v\u00e0 Thiago Silva \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 30. Marquinhos l\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/18/Brazil-1-1-Thuy-Sy.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neymar-chi-trich-trong-tai-sau-khi-brazil-bi-cam-hoa-469-188790.html\">Neymar ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau khi Brazil b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-ban-thua-oan-va-mat-11m-marcelo-noi-gi-421-188788.html\">Nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua oan v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t 11m, Marcelo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"307","checkdouble":"188796"},{"date":"10:03 18/06","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/mu-chot-gia-60-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Martial c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/MU-muon-mua-Willian-cua-Chelsea-thay-the-Anthony-Martial-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial s\u1ebd d\u1ee9t \u00e1o chia tay MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Martial. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u1edf Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ef1u sao Monaco \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u00a0\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-chi-80-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-anthony-martial-180-173928.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real quan t\u00e2m Martial</span>, PSG, Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh l\u00e0 Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho nh\u1eafm Willian thay Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 Martial ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea san sang trao doi giua Willian va Martial\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Willian v\u00e0 Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/chelsea-san-sang-trao-doi-cau-thu-voi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Willian thay Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge b\u1edfi m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Conte.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Mourinho khi\u1ebfn The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"306","checkdouble":"188797"},{"date":"10:18 18/06","title":"Liverpool s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Fifa World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 18/6 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV v\u00e0 HTV v\u00e0 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng internet</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 186 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 186 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-hom-nay-18-6.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u0110V B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn ni\u1ec1m vui</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00f4m nay, l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tay khi 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ea3ng G \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady 2 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico v\u00e0 Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng F, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Mexico h\u00f4m qua th\u00ec b\u1ea3ng F s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1ea5t trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<h3>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay</h3>\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-collapse:&#10; collapse;width:100%\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n    <colgroup><col width=\"184\" style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:6729;width:138pt\" />  <col width=\"115\" style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:4205;width:86pt\" />  <col width=\"273\" style=\"mso-width-source:us