ink href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Patrice Evra c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Milinkovic-Savic ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Man United h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>MU li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Man United trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia t\u1ea1i World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ph\u00eda Lazio mong mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Real Madrid v\u00e0 Juventus c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Patrice Evra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Patrice Evra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/evra-len-tieng-canh-bao-milinkovicsavic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Milinkovic-Savic nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Evra</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Man United theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Milinkovic-Savic, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Patrice Evra cho hay:<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn m\u1ed7i khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Manchester United. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ti\u00ean quy\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ebft v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng \u2018Evra, c\u1eadu s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Man United nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng\u2019, th\u00ec t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eady n\u00ean n\u1ebfu Milinkovic-Savic c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn Man United v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ebft v\u00ec CLB, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Milinkovic-Savic ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00e0 Henrik Larsson l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Savic \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Serbia h\u00f4m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho Man United. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i pha b\u00f3ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCosta Rica kh\u00f4ng cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t t\u00edch trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Costa Rica 0-1 Serbia (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Costa-1-0-Serbia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ngoai-hang-anh-la-ben-do-hoan-hao-voi-milinkovicsavic-172-188720.html\">Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Milinkovic-Savic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/milinkovicsavic-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-den-mu-184-188100.html\">Milinkovic-Savic l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"304","checkdouble":"188799"},{"date":"10:33 18/06","title":"Ch\u00f3 ti\u00ean tri Psychic d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Anh th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/cho-tien-tri-psychic-du-doan-anh-thang-tran-mo-man-world-cup-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 ti\u00ean tri mang t\u00ean Psychic d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Tunisia vs Anh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Tunisia v\u1edbi Anh, di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 1h ng\u00e0y 19/6 (theo gi\u1edd H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i).</h2><h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cdv-mexico-tao-dong-dat-khi-mung-chien-tich-thang-duc-421-188800.html\">C\u0110V Mexico t\u1ea1o ... \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t khi m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/wenger-chi-ra-2-van-de-cua-brazil-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si-469-188796.html\">Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra 2 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Brazil sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-nga-coi-thuong-salah-truoc-man-tiep-ai-cap-421-188793.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Salah tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp Ai C\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neymar-chi-trich-trong-tai-sau-khi-brazil-bi-cam-hoa-469-188790.html\">Neymar ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau khi Brazil b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-ban-thua-oan-va-mat-11m-marcelo-noi-gi-421-188788.html\">Nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua oan v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t 11m, Marcelo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"303","checkdouble":"188801"},{"date":"10:46 18/06","title":"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 18/6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-186.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Fifa World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 18/6 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV v\u00e0 HTV v\u00e0 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng internet</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 186 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 186 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-hom-nay-18-6.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u0110V B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn ni\u1ec1m vui</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00f4m nay, l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tay khi 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ea3ng G \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady 2 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico v\u00e0 Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng F, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Mexico h\u00f4m qua th\u00ec b\u1ea3ng F s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1ea5t trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<h3>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay</h3>\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-collapse:&#10; collapse;width:100%\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n    <colgroup><col width=\"184\" style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:6729;width:138pt\" />  <col width=\"115\" style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:4205;width:86pt\" />  <col width=\"273\" style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:9984;width:205pt\" />  </colgroup>\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr height=\"20\" style=\"height:15.0pt\">\r\n            <td height=\"20\" class=\"xl63\" width=\"184\" style=\"height: 15pt; width: 138pt; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-top: 2px; text-align: center;\" data-sheets-value=\"{\"><strong>TR\u1eacN   \u0110\u1ea4U</strong></td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl63\" width=\"115\" style=\"width: 86pt; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-top: 2px; text-align: center;\" data-sheets-value=\"{\"><stron