e><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111ua tranh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ecf s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd lu m\u1edd m\u1ecdi t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span>. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh, n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng n\u1ed5 hat-trick h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh, n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng n\u1ed5 hat-trick h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/harry-kane-nong-long-no-hattrick-nhu-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Tunisia vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 Harry Kane, m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c cho danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau khi theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3ng B \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 hay nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Tunisia vs Anh c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng 25 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB Tottenham: \u201cCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u1edbi Ronaldo. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u01b0u ti\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch chung c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n, t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m to l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ngh\u00eanh \u0111\u00f3n Tunisia t\u1ed1i nay. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u m\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Ch\u00e2u Phi, trong khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ti\u1ebfn c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ea7y tr\u1eadt c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-tunisia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-196-thu-da-keu-dot-dung-xit-421-188765.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1862018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-tunisia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-196-thu-da-keu-dot-dung-xit-421-188765.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tunisia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 19/6): Th\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau, \u0111\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eebng x\u1ecbt</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tunisia vs Anh b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018: Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh trang l\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"301","checkdouble":"188803"},{"date":"11:54 18/06","title":"Messi cay c\u00fa ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \"l\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i\" c\u1ee7a Iceland","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/messi-cay-cu-chi-trich-loi-choi-lay-loi-cua-iceland.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Barcelona kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1 Iceland trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u1ee8ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Argentina ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1ecb t\u00e2n binh Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Lionel Messi s\u1eafm vai t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecfng \u0103n qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 cay c\u00fa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 cay c\u00fa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/messi-cay-cu-chi-trich-loi-choi-lay-loi-cua-iceland.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland, cay c\u00fa ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00ednh si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Barcelona l\u1ea1i quay ra cay c\u00fa ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u201cl\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i\u201d c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Messi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/argentina-11-iceland-le-hien-nhien-sao-con-phai-goi-la-co-tich-421-188680.html\">Argentina 1-1 Iceland</span>:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cIceland v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u1edf h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c n\u00e9m bi\u00ean. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Argentina c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ed1n d\u0129 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m Iceland.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Iceland, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Croatia, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-bao-ve-messi-chi-trich-nhan-to-khac-cua-argentina-421-188795.html\">Maradona b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-11-iceland-khong-phai-bo-dao-nha-ronaldo-argentina-messi-moi-la-doi-bong-mot-nguoi-421-188679.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i B\u1ed3-Ronaldo, ch\u00ednh Argentina-Messi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"300","checkdouble":"188805"},{"date":"11:11 18/06","title":"Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Martial kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n... v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/6/mourinho-khang-dinh-martial-khong-phai-de-ban-voi-gia-thap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1eadn t\u00fai b\u1ee5i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn World Cup, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Mourinho ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Martial trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMartial kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/martial-lo-dau-hieu-la-ngay-roi-mu-khong-con-xa-172-186964.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anthony Martial \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y \u0111en t\u1ed1i nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</span>. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, khi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-tien-dao-martial-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-mu-172-188440.html\" target=\"_blank\">Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford</span> ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Man United l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ee9c \u00e9p n\u00e0o t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford, k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa, Martial ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i khi M.U mong mu\u1ed1n. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia tay t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y l\u00e0 g\u00ec? \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1eeba l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Martial ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Martial tri \u00e2n HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/co-doi-bong-chi-88-trieu-bang-mua-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Martial ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mirror, HLV Jose Mourinho ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Martial 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i trong ph\u1ea1m vi Premier League. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd The Sun c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111ang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 M.U n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n The Blues c\u0169ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, ch\u1ee9 quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng &ldquo;b\u00e1n m\u00e1u&rdquo; cho k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Mourinho ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Martial, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Old Trafford ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0, v\u1edbi c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 bao nhi\u00eau m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Phap-2-1-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/martial-lo-dau-hieu-la-ngay-roi-mu-khong-con-xa-172-186964.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/martial-lo-dau-hieu-la-ngay-roi-mu-khong-con-xa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/martial-lo-dau-hieu-la-ngay-roi-mu-khong-con-xa-172-186964.html\">Martial l\u1ed9 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u &ldquo;l\u1ea1&rdquo;: T\u1eeb ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh k\u1ebb b\u1ecb Mourinho ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial r\u1eddi MU ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf, sau khi anh khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf &ldquo;t\u00e1 h\u1ecfa&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-gia-60-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial-172-188797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/mu-chot-gia-60-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-gia-60-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial-172-188797.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Martial</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"299","checkdouble":"188806"},{"date":"11:12 18/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 18/6: Neymar tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng x\u00e0i VAR","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/ngay-hom-nay-186.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (18/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng x\u00e0i VAR</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Steven Zuber v\u1edbi Miranda tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y sau trong b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Brazil, \"Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3o x\u1ee9 samba\" c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u00ean b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khi anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Rostov Arena r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 186 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 186 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/wenger-chi-ra-2-van-de-cua-brazil-sau-tran-hoa-thuy-si.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Joachim Loew l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1, hu\u1ea5n lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Joachim Loew gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico theo k\u00e8m Toni Kroos r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111eo b\u00e1m nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng F. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 186 Neymar tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng x\u00e0i VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 186 Neymar tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng x\u00e0i VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-ngay-186-Neymar-trach-trong-tai-khong-xai-VAR-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Joachim Loew</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Xem th\u00eam</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi-465-188760.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi-465-188760.html\">HLV Joachim Low: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Hirving Lozano n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</h2>\r\n<div>Sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi ghi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hirving Lozano ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ESPN. Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, Mexico \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, song \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0. Hirving Lozano l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u201cqu\u00fd nh\u01b0 v\u00e0ng\u201d cho tuy\u1ec3n Mexico \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lozano ghi ban mo ti so trong tran dau giua Duc vs Mexico.\" title=\"Lozano ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/lozano.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lozano</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Brazil?</h2>\r\n<div>Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Brazil 1-1 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Vladimir Petkovic cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Brazil l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u1eady n\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00fd gi\u00e1, n\u00ean t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Vladimir Petkovic hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ede v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ec9 thua 1 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-thuy-sy-noi-gi-sau-chien-tich-cam-hoa-brazil-421-188781.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-thuy-sy-noi-gi-sau-chien-tich-cam-hoa-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-thuy-sy-noi-gi-sau-chien-tich-cam-hoa-brazil-421-188781.html\">HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Brazil</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Vladimir Petkovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 54 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh NHM s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1eb1ng con m\u1eaft kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi Brazil ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<div>\"T\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\", hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Tite chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. \"\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a World Cup, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhanh h\u01a1n\", v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Brazil ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E khi \u0110T Serbia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Costa Rica v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-vs-thuy-si-su-dai-kho-cua-tite-da-lam-hai-selecao-421-188772.html\">Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129: S\u1ef1 d\u1ea1i kh\u1edd c\u1ee7a Tite \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i Selecao</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kane l\u1ea5y Ronaldo l\u00e0m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau</h2>\r\n<div>Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n t\u1edd Goal, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u201cngang h\u00e0ng\u201d v\u1edbi CR7 trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. \u201cAnh \u1ea5y t\u1ea1o cho t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Hy v\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp Ronaldo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane muon DT Anh len ngoi vo dich\" title=\"Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/harry-kane-nong-long-no-hattrick-nhu-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kane</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Croatia nh\u1edd Rakitic \u201chi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf\u201d</h2>\r\n<div>Sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, Croatia s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng khi ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zlatko Dalic ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 Leo Messi v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch khi\u1ebfn si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y \u201ct\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u201d. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Iceland, HLV n\u00e0y c\u00f2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb Ivan Rakitic - tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Messi t\u1ea1i Barcelona.</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois \u201ct\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c\u201d Hazard</h2>\r\n<div>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u201ct\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, Eden Hazard trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. \u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Eden \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m nay v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady trong 3 tu\u1ea7n qua. World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Eden\u201d.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"298","checkdouble":"188807"},{"date":"07:44 18/06","title":"HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-thuy-sy-noi-gi-sau-chien-tich-cam-hoa-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hai \u0111\u1ed9i?</h2><br>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: M\u1ed9t tr\u1eddi m\u1ed9t v\u1ef1c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\" target=\"_blank\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i </span>t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh th\u00eam c\u1ea3 V-League 2017 v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u00fap QG 2018 th\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i n\u00ean con s\u1ed1 20.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n sau 13 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Thanh H\u00f3a hay HAGL. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u1ebb kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Moses gi\u00e0u c\u01a1 b\u1eafp khu trung tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Oseni \u0111ang l\u00e0 hung th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 V-League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Sau-vong-14-V-League-2018-Ha-Noi,-HAGL-dong-loat-nga-ngua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-1 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u00edt ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi 7 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 13.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd ghi 15 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec gi\u1ea3i, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean con s\u1ed1 24 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u1ea1i theo m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eady m\u00e0 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m l\u00e0 Da Sylva l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 &lsquo;v\u01b0\u01a1n vai&rsquo; \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League 2018, m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay 12 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u01a1 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ea1ch?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi xa l\u1ea1 vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n hay SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 &lsquo;anh em m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0&rsquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ed7 Quang Hi\u1ec3n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1eddi \u0111\u00f4 v\u00e0o Nam c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby v\u00e0 t\u1eebng n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n Giang \u0110\u00f4ng, c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0 b\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y r\u00e0ng bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i V-League. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 &lsquo;ru\u1ed9t th\u1ecbt&rsquo; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e9p d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn 100% tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u trung th\u1ef1c, cao th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi thua dam Sai Gon o vong 14 V-League 2018.\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ea1ch \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, Bongda24h xin kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 n\u00eau ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c quan t\u00e2m sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra chuy\u1ec7n cho \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i V-League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a</span><br>\r\nV\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu thua \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. N\u00f3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nHLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"297","checkdouble":"188781"},{"date":"08:06 18/06","title":"Sao Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ednh tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 v\u1edbi Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sao-thuy-sy-phu-nhan-vao-bong-mang-tinh-triet-ha-voi-neymar.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Valon Behrami n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ednh tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Neymar \u0111i v\u00e0o k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Brazil c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. Selecao c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Coutinho, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 Steven Zuber g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Valon Behrami n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Neymar sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Valon Behrami n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Neymar sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Valon-Behrami-noi-ve-Neymar-sau-tran-Brazil-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i 10 l\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. H\u00f2a 1-1 trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1eabn r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf v\u1edbi Brazil, song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb NHM.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 4 l\u1ea7n 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, ngo\u00e0i ra Neymar c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 4 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i. Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n. Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Neymar trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 Alan Shearer n\u0103m 1998 (11 l\u1ea7n).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00fa v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 t\u1ecf ra \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn, r\u1ea5t may anh kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ednh tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 v\u1edbi Neymar</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Valon Behrami n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ednh tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petkovic phu nhan vao bong ac y voi Neymar\" title=\"Petkovic ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1edbi Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/sao-thuy-sy-phu-nhan-vao-bong-mang-tinh-triet-ha-voi-neymar.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Behrami ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1edbi Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Neymar. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u0111au&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Vladimir Petkovic c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1edbi Neymar. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i t\u1eeb xa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, song HLV Petkovic tin r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Manuel Akanji, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i tin \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-thuy-sy-noi-gi-sau-chien-tich-cam-hoa-brazil-421-188781.html\" target=\"_blank\">Vladimir Petkovic c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</span>, \u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/18/Brazil-1-1-Thuy-Sy.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"296","checkdouble":"188782"},{"date":"07:23 18/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (18/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1862018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; paddin